data.description:
Welcome to this stunning Lennar Model home in the highly desirable Glen Loma community. Built in 2021, this home offers 5 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and approximately 2984 square feet of living space. With Solar power, this home is both energy-efficient and beautiful. 

 The main level features a formal living room, a bedroom perfect for overnight guests, a full bathroom, and a family room/dining area. The open-concept kitchen is a chef's dream with granite countertops, custom cabinetry, and built-in stainless-steel appliances. 

 Upstairs, you'll find four more bedrooms, including the luxurious owner's suite with a spa-like bathroom and his-and-her walk-in closets. The backyard is perfect for hosting parties and gatherings. 

 Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your dream home.
